data.description: Priced in a range between 589-599k. Welcome to your coastal retreat in Oceanside by San Luis Rey River trail while close to the beach as well. Located in the popular Brisbane community, this move-in ready home offers convenient one level living with plenty of natural light, a spacious open floor plan with private balcony, indoor laundry, a cozy fireplace, and an attached garage with extra parking space. The complex features a pool and spa, a dog run/park area, play structure and in close proximity to restaurants, coffee shops, retail shopping, and parks. This is an amazing opportunity to own a rarely available end-unit in an amazing location. The interior was repainted and recently replaced the hot water heater and upgraded HVAC system with an energy efficient unit with a special air purification feature. This home is in meticulous condition and has been wonderfully maintained. Easy access to I-5, Hwy 76 & the Vandergrift/ back gate of Camp Pendleton. Close By: Mance Bucanan Park & San Luis Rey Bike Trail. VA and FHA Approved.
